With AI (Using ChatGPT API)

Instead of collecting data and training your own large model, you use a pre-trained AI model through an API.

The red crosses on Data Collection and Train indicate that these steps are already done by the provider of the AI model.

What changes?
❌ No Data Collection

The AI model has already been trained on a vast amount of text, so you don't need to collect billions of examples.

❌ No Training

The model has already learned language, grammar, reasoning, and many tasks. You simply send prompts to it.

✅ Only Deployment

Your job is mainly to:

Connect your application to the API
Design good prompts
Build the user interface
Test the application

This can often be completed in about 2 weeks instead of several months.

