Example
Traditional Translation AI

To build an English-to-Hindi translator yourself, you would need to:

Collect millions of English-Hindi sentence pairs.
Train a Transformer model on powerful GPUs.
Evaluate and improve the model.
Deploy it for users.

This process could take many months.

Using ChatGPT API

With a pre-trained model:

Create a simple application.
Send the English text to the ChatGPT API.
Receive the Hindi translation.
Display it to the user.

Because the language understanding is already built into the model, you focus on integrating it into your application rather than training it.

